[05:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Now, limitations: only handles full-body motion,&nbsp;&nbsp; no facial gestures, no hand articulation,&nbsp; I think that is quite clear. It is not yet&nbsp;&nbsp; an end to end solution as it also relies&nbsp; on an off-the-shelf SLAM method, that is,&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[05:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'simultaneous localization and mapping. This&nbsp; helps extracting useful information out of&nbsp;&nbsp; the videos like the camera position and direction&nbsp; and hand it off to this AI technique. In short:&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[05:36] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it cannot do every processing needed alone, but&nbsp; it is close. Now, this has a heavy diffusion&nbsp;&nbsp; backbone, it needs 5 denoising steps, so I think&nbsp; it might not be real time yet, but nearly there.'

